data.description: Welcome to 3601 Spinnaker Drive in Anchorage, Alaska, where comfort and convenience meet in this beautiful 4-bedroom, 3-bathroom home spanning 2,102 square feet. With a spacious layout and modern amenities throughout, including updated kitchen appliances and fixtures, this residence offers a warm and inviting atmosphere filled with natural light. Outside, the private backyard provides a serene space for outdoor gatherings and relaxation. Situated in a desirable neighborhood, enjoy easy access to parks, shopping centers, restaurants, and excellent schools, making it the perfect place to call home in Anchorage.
